data.description: Welcome to this inviting home nestled on a corner lot in the Park Place Community. This property features a 3-sided brick exterior and a spacious living area with an open floor plan, a comfortable size primary bedroom with dual vanities in the primary bathroom. Enjoy the spacious backyard with a covered patio for outdoor family gatherings. Neighborhood Amenities include a pool, basketball court, park and playground. Quick access to Loop 1604, Hwy 90, Loop 410, Hwy 151, Lackland AFB and the city of Castroville.  Minutes away from nearby Dove Creek and Alamo Ranch shopping centers, restaurants, and movie theaters. Schedule your showing today!
